    public final class DomainRegistrantTransferCommand

    In cases where the legal registrant of a domain name has changed, this class should be used to request a transfer of registrant. This is a different action to correcting extension data which was originally specified incorrectly, and should only be used in the situation described. Use this class to generate a standards-compliant XML document, given simple input parameters. The toXML() method in Command serialises this object to XML.
